name: Philactica
overview:
Providing Phlatelists worldwide with quality collector material since 1980.

We offer a platform for stamp collectors to Buy and Sell quality material on a philately only site.

Currently representing British Africa, New Zealand and Europe with a little Asian. Sets, Areogrammes, Postal history, Covers, FDCs, basically anything philatelic. We do not entertain single used listed stamps after 1960 or USED modern material with wavy or killer obliteration and are respectfully declined as an individual listing. Such grouped can be offered as bulk, mixture or packet material.

View for yourself the great selection already available as Mint never hinge or used sets etc.

Good hunting.
